*"1244-00000298-01Z" is silkscreened on the board populating this entry.
The board is using capacitors from three manufacturers: '''S.Y''', '''Canicon''', and '''Suncap'''. :The model noted on the label is V1.0A.
The power adapter included with the US version is a '''DVE''' DSC-6PFA-05 :FUS 050100 (100-240VAC ~ 50/60Hz, 0.2A -> 5VDC, 1A).
